<emphasis bold="true" box="[2037,2111,2485,2522]" pageId="27" pageNumber="24">and</emphasis>
&quot;sifted from 
<emphasis box="[1466,1530,2530,2567]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="24">soil</emphasis>
.&quot;
</paragraph>
